    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dreadwoods Gatekeeper 将提供 4–5 小时的游戏体验，包含一份守门人模拟工作、一部充满角色与层次的悬疑惊悚故事，以及需要与主角一起掌握的弓箭战斗技巧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389020/extras/d0763791da75b8c0824399fd2a440eeb.poster.avif?t=1772030765\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389020/extras/d0763791da75b8c0824399fd2a440eeb.webm?t=1772030765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389020/extras/d0763791da75b8c0824399fd2a440eeb.mp4?t=1772030765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你来到小镇 Dreadwoods，接任守门人的工作。前任守卫被杀，镇民们紧抱着古怪的迷信，每当修道院的钟声响起，他们便封锁房门。与此同时，关于森林里潜伏着怪物的传言也在扩散。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法包括：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守门管理：与镇民交谈、开关大门、检查商队和他们的文件、批准或拒绝入境，并进行维护工作。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389020/extras/7827fae0beb24ad9ba0d28d61233b82a.poster.avif?t=1772030765\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389020/extras/7827fae0beb24ad9ba0d28d61233b82a.webm?t=1772030765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389020/extras/7827fae0beb24ad9ba0d28d61233b82a.mp4?t=1772030765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事：熟悉小镇及其居民。结交朋友或树立敌人。Dreadwoods 是一座孤立的小镇，落后于文明，隐藏着许多秘密和荒诞的迷信。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389020/extras/09b9105f2f4c628fe34bf1f3ba225c81.poster.avif?t=1772030765\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389020/extras/09b9105f2f4c628fe34bf1f3ba225c81.webm?t=1772030765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389020/extras/09b9105f2f4c628fe34bf1f3ba225c81.mp4?t=1772030765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巡逻：主角并非战士，但在巡逻森林时，他必须掌握弓箭，以保护自己和他人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389020/extras/36f614e88d35b5dba3782634b859ebcd.poster.avif?t=1772030765\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389020/extras/36f614e88d35b5dba3782634b859ebcd.webm?t=1772030765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389020/extras/36f614e88d35b5dba3782634b859ebcd.mp4?t=1772030765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将游戏加入愿望清单，并关注以获取第一版试玩发布的通知。</p>",
